I'd prefer it if Prodigy changed his Astrotrain's name... its just not 
the same when you change an original character's name, and the 
fact that he hasn't submitted a profile. I kinda figured that if somone 
has a character they should play their character or have some sort 
of way to distinguish the fact that the character exists. I will 
change the name is necessary, but I disagree.

Perhaps you should ask people(the ones who haven't already) to 
send in their profiles in the my friend and I submitted. Its fairly 
simple and the site at the bottom of every one of our character's 
profiles has many good ideas and description.

Also, is the site down right now?

rAuq (the A is capitalized, not the R) =P
